{"tid":601857,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[推坑]The Caster Chronicles(魔法少女Caster) - 日系魔法少女TCG","createTime":"2018-03-22T14:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T05:30:38.000Z","uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"615634d681470b716edbd31d45416a4947a4ff80","tid":601857,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"The Caster Chronicles 是Force of Will社在半年前出的一隻日系TCG<br />\n而家香港已經有代理，除左聚集到一班玩家同埋店鋪以外<br />\n仲會周圍搞比賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheCasterChroniclesTCGHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheCasterChroniclesTCGHK%2F&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1IS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=97e1c7f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TheCasterChroniclesTCGHK/</a><br />\n想玩一隻類Magic囡囡遊戲，ＴＣＣ絕對係唯一選擇<br />\n<br />\n香港代理同時做中日英三個版本，市面上流通的ＴＣＣ卡都可以用<br />\n（除左日本限定ＰＲ，全球其他地方都唔用得）<br />\n<br />\n遊戲系統就是Magic+召喚王<br />\n<br />\n一開始會有七張寶珠(血)<br />\n玩家受到傷害就會彈上手，如果有綻放（英：Break）就可以無條件施放<br />\n當玩家無寶珠而再受到傷害就會敗北（無珠之後要再入一度）<br />\n<br />\n生物（日:怪異，中:僕從）進埸可以馬上攻擊（沒有召喚失調這回事）<br />\n玩家可以倒置生物作防禦狀態<br />\n要直接攻擊玩家的時候必須要先攻擊防守狀態的生物（除非他有傲慢）<br />\n（當然也可以攻擊其他生物）<br />\n<br />\n魔法少女除了是一塊產魔力的地以外<br />\n還有很多實用效果需要依賴魔法少女<br />\n（例如橫置自己抽牌／檢索／殺怪）<br />\n<br />\n詳細規則可以去睇睇說明書，而家應該有中文版<br />\n<a href=\"http://mtdtaiwan.wixsite.com/index-caster/blank-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmtdtaiwan.wixsite.com%2Findex-caster%2Fblank-1&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1IS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=d5f9defe\" target=\"_blank\">http://mtdtaiwan.wixsite.com/index-caster/blank-1</a><br />\n（台灣官網）<br />\n<br />\n雖然初期官方搞錯重點，把生物都畫成怪物樣子（其實有些還很順眼的）<br />\n不過在魔法少女育成計劃合作後，官方終於發現「前排生物也應該同樣都是妹子」<br />\n所以第二彈馬上把第一彈的黑歷史怪物重印成妹子<br />\n然後再推出一個結魂（融合＋超量）系統把魔法少女推上前線<br />\n把一隻定位不明的遊戲，變成一隻類Magic玩法的囡囡Game<br />\n再加上香港代理的努力，令TCC起死回生<br />\n拉攏了一班Magic玩家入坑<br />\n<br />\n下篇講下卡圖變化"},{"pid":"29c06f3493a8c132736fd50e9907075cb9561a4f","tid":601857,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:19:02.000Z","msg":"左：2彈囡囡<br />\n右：1彈怪物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/221753_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F221753_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=6f81f156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/221629_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F221629_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=dffa2eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n私心貼幾張個人覺得改得幾索的<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/221847_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F221847_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=83024005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/221855_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F221855_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=2965e3e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e715853bb267bd1e4a5f29f2310befc452e59ba","tid":601857,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29c06f3493a8c132736fd50e9907075cb9561a4f","tid":601857,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:19:02.000Z","msg":"左：2彈囡囡<br />\n右：1彈怪物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/221753_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F221753_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=6f81f156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/221629_fa63fca