"pid":"ec4214b7126527f2523814ad2d8940c813bcd401","tid":601857,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bb9e84cf81f022ed9bac2fc666add300c2a52b6","tid":601857,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:20:55.000Z","msg":"嘩 好毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:45:46.000Z","msg":"無你ga事<br />\n<br />\n話明係魔法少女game,當然多囡囡<br />\n之前隻game堆怪物你又唔入黎捧埸"},{"pid":"94318792aebf471f85831470264a3a9e16f711be","tid":601857,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/230026_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F230026_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=c7d06b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講下結魂<br />\n2彈一個拿黎<del>賣萌</del>爆發的系統<br />\n總括黎講 係將兩個魔法少女融合<br />\n融合素材會放係結魂怪下面<br />\n甩一張再發參戰效或代離場一次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是放在Extra deck的結魂怪異<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/230049_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F230049_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=6f2a1839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結魂所需要的素材係結魂怪異上面寫著<br />\nXX心YY<br />\n<br />\n支付兩點任意有色魔力<br />\n係手牌或戰場上將對應魔法少女犧牲<br />\n就可以係額外卡組召喚結魂怪<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/233148_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F233148_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=be5636c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這隻結魂入場效係對手丟棄一張手牌<br />\n結魂後有兩個素材 一口氣移除可以開3次削手效果<br />\n加上她打中寶珠可以抽牌<br />\n可以一口氣拉開牌差<br />\n<br />\nSecret版（爆衫）結魂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/234031_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F234031_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=3bbcf7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似有唔知3種定6種唔同樣的secret結魂<br />\n<br />\n英文版有聖光<del>其實我覺得有聖光先似合緊體</del><br />\n<del>個人覺得白卡卡圖最靚 但抽到secret無理由唔用<br />\n</del>"},{"pid":"b0387ab5c43d16005df7212e87769eb6067ba697","tid":601857,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ec329a8b2a6b6af31a445791f8aaddf6007fbd0","tid":601857,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a6c3cbe199d4d94627a0883978ee2a877944d13","tid":601857,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"得閒講下點召喚王法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"召喚王都係地牌<br />\n同埋七度甲,有綻放<br />\n同埋無得用怪接攻擊 (blocker係技能)<br />\n<br />\n不過召喚王可以用任何卡做地,魔法少女就跟番magic有地牌(魔法少女)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:49:16.000Z","msg":"你講緊邊個召喚王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDuel master?"},{"pid":"2c8e14f5107ff7930478ad472d2d49fc874205ac","tid":601857,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"聽日係屯門 金豐遊玩王有比賽/試玩會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1754047514615378/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F1754047514615378%2F&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1IS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=9d6b6ae0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1754047514615378/</a><br />\n<br />\n星期六係荔枝角都有一埸比賽/試玩會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1724486890942971/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F1724486890942971%2F&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1IS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=2b20c795\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1724486890942971/</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣就過黎打下deck<br />\n<br />\n打住咁多先<br />\n下次講下魔法少女育成系列"},{"pid":"f24ff7c4385cc7351974c361ba21ada109ab8f4a","tid":601857,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s